    {
      "title": "<span id=\"#11622\" class=\"scroll-m-16 text-3xl font-bold flex items-center\"><h1 class=\"inline !mb-1 scroll-m-16 text-3xl font-bold\">especially</h1><div class=\"pl-2 flex-1 text-textSecondary text-xl font-serif\">(adv.)</div></span>",
      "html": "<p>约于1400年，源自于 <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of especial \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/especial\">especial</a> 和 <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of -ly \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/-ly#etymonline_v_32027\">-ly</a> (2)。</p>"
